<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04702</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INCREASING THE PENALTY FOR VIOLATION OF THE PROVISIONS OF REPUBLIC ACT 8484</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : " Access Devises Regulation Act Of 1998 " Amendment</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to amend Sec.10 of R.A.8484 otherwise known as the "Access Devises Regulation Act of 1998", making it a non-bailable offense. Increases the fines for this offense anywhere from P3,000,000 to P5,000,000, instead of the present P10,000.


</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ATIENZA, JOSE JR. L.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-12-21</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON REVISION OF LAWS ON 2017-01-16</td></tr></table>